{"block_id": "B005", "document_id": "0001193125-14-455030", "ordinal": 5, "start_line": 1281, "end_line": 1282, "raw_text": "In 2007 and 2009, the Company received unsolicited indications of interest to acquire Penford from two parties engaged in the Company\u0092s\nindustry. In each case, the Company entered into a confidentiality agreement and engaged in discussions and exchanged information with the party expressing interest. These discussions did not result in offers to acquire the Company.", "clean_text": "In 2007 and 2009, the Company received unsolicited indications of interest to acquire Penford from two parties engaged in the Company\u0092s industry. In each case, the Company entered into a confidentiality agreement and engaged in discussions and exchanged information with the party expressing interest. These discussions did not result in offers to acquire the Company.", "is_heading": false, "page_break_before": false, "page_break_after": false, "date_mentions": [], "entity_mentions": [{"raw_text": "the Company", "entity_type": "party_alias"}], "evidence_density": 2, "temporal_phase": "bidding"}
