{"block_id": "B081", "document_id": "0001193125-14-455030", "ordinal": 81, "start_line": 1603, "end_line": 1605, "raw_text": "and lower EBITDA than was projected in the materials previously provided to Ingredion from Penford\u0092s strategic plan. Later on October 11, members of the accounting teams at Penford and\nIngredion, as well as their respective financial advisors, Deutsche Bank and J. P. Morgan Securities, held a conference call to discuss Penford\u0092s 2014 draft financial statements, including the determination of the final numbers used in the draft\nfinancial statements. Also on October 11, 2014 Milbank and Sidley Austin discussed the proposed voting and support agreement.", "clean_text": "and lower EBITDA than was projected in the materials previously provided to Ingredion from Penford\u0092s strategic plan. Later on October 11, members of the accounting teams at Penford and Ingredion, as well as their respective financial advisors, Deutsche Bank and J. P. Morgan Securities, held a conference call to discuss Penford\u0092s 2014 draft financial statements, including the determination of the final numbers used in the draft financial statements. Also on October 11, 2014 Milbank and Sidley Austin discussed the proposed voting and support agreement.", "is_heading": false, "page_break_before": false, "page_break_after": false, "date_mentions": [{"raw_text": "October", "normalized": null, "precision": "unknown"}, {"raw_text": "October 11, 2014", "normalized": "2014-10-11", "precision": "exact_day"}], "entity_mentions": [], "evidence_density": 2, "temporal_phase": "bidding"}
{"block_id": "B082", "document_id": "0001193125-14-455030", "ordinal": 82, "start_line": 1607, "end_line": 1607, "raw_text": "On", "clean_text": "On", "is_heading": true, "page_break_before": false, "page_break_after": false, "date_mentions": [], "entity_mentions": [], "evidence_density": 3, "temporal_phase": "outcome"}
{"block_id": "B083", "document_id": "0001193125-14-455030", "ordinal": 83, "start_line": 1608, "end_line": 1610, "raw_text": "October 12, 2014, members of the accounting teams at Penford and Ingredion, as well as their respective financial advisors, held another conference call to discuss the reconciliation of the 2014 draft financial statements compared to the\nmaterials previously provided to Ingredion from Penford\u0092s strategic plan. Also on October 12, 2014, Milbank discussed the voting and support agreement to be entered into by SEACOR with Sidley Austin, and distributed a revised draft of such\nvoting and support agreement, and Sidley Austin and Perkins Coie had a teleconference to discuss certain open items in the merger agreement.", "clean_text": "October 12, 2014, members of the accounting teams at Penford and Ingredion, as well as their respective financial advisors, held another conference call to discuss the reconciliation of the 2014 draft financial statements compared to the materials previously provided to Ingredion from Penford\u0092s strategic plan. Also on October 12, 2014, Milbank discussed the voting and support agreement to be entered into by SEACOR with Sidley Austin, and distributed a revised draft of such voting and support agreement, and Sidley Austin and Perkins Coie had a teleconference to discuss certain open items in the merger agreement.", "is_heading": false, "page_break_before": false, "page_break_after": false, "date_mentions": [{"raw_text": "October 12, 2014", "normalized": "2014-10-12", "precision": "exact_day"}], "entity_mentions": [], "evidence_density": 3, "temporal_phase": "outcome"}
{"block_id": "B084", "document_id": "0001193125-14-455030", "ordinal": 84, "start_line": 1612, "end_line": 1614, "raw_text": "On October 13, 2014, Mr. Malkoski and Mr. Fortnum discussed the 2014 draft financial statements as compared with the\nprojections included in the materials provided to Ingredion from Penford\u0092s strategic plan. Mr. Fortnum stated that the figures reflected in the 2014 draft financial statements might have an adverse impact on Ingredion\u0092s view of the\nvaluation of the Company. Also on October 13, 2014, Milbank and Sidley Austin discussed and traded drafts of the voting and support agreement to be entered into by SEACOR.", "clean_text": "On October 13, 2014, Mr. Malkoski and Mr. Fortnum discussed the 2014 draft financial statements as compared with the projections included in the materials provided to Ingredion from Penford\u0092s strategic plan. Mr. Fortnum stated that the figures reflected in the 2014 draft financial statements might have an adverse impact on Ingredion\u0092s view of the valuation of the Company. Also on October 13, 2014, Milbank and Sidley Austin discussed and traded drafts of the voting and support agreement to be entered into by SEACOR.", "is_heading": false, "page_break_before": false, "page_break_after": false, "date_mentions": [{"raw_text": "October 13, 2014", "normalized": "2014-10-13", "precision": "exact_day"}], "entity_mentions": [{"raw_text": "the Company", "entity_type": "party_alias"}], "evidence_density": 1, "temporal_phase": "bidding"}
{"block_id": "B085", "document_id": "0001193125-14-455030", "ordinal": 85, "start_line": 1616, "end_line": 1617, "raw_text": "On October 13, 2014, Deutsche Bank had a discussion with representatives of Party A, who indicated that its value range for a potential\ntransaction had been reduced from $17.50 - $18.00 per share to $16.00 - $18.00 per share, due to increased volatility in the markets.", "clean_text": "On October 13, 2014, Deutsche Bank had a discussion with representatives of Party A, who indicated that its value range for a potential transaction had been reduced from $17.50 - $18.00 per share to $16.00 - $18.00 per share, due to increased volatility in the markets.", "is_heading": false, "page_break_before": false, "page_break_after": false, "date_mentions": [{"raw_text": "October 13, 2014", "normalized": "2014-10-13", "precision": "exact_day"}], "entity_mentions": [{"raw_text": "Party A", "entity_type": "party_alias"}], "evidence_density": 3, "temporal_phase": "bidding"}
{"block_id": "B086", "document_id": "0001193125-14-455030", "ordinal": 86, "start_line": 1619, "end_line": 1620, "raw_text": "Also on October 13, 2014, Sidley Austin circulated a revised draft of the merger agreement to Perkins Coie. Perkins Coie and Sidley\nAustin also discussed the draft disclosure letter and later on October 13, 2014, Perkins Coie and Sidley Austin exchanged revised drafts of the disclosure letter.", "clean_text": "Also on October 13, 2014, Sidley Austin circulated a revised draft of the merger agreement to Perkins Coie. Perkins Coie and Sidley Austin also discussed the draft disclosure letter and later on October 13, 2014, Perkins Coie and Sidley Austin exchanged revised drafts of the disclosure letter.", "is_heading": false, "page_break_before": false, "page_break_after": false, "date_mentions": [{"raw_text": "October 13, 2014", "normalized": "2014-10-13", "precision": "exact_day"}], "entity_mentions": [], "evidence_density": 2, "temporal_phase": "outcome"}
{"block_id": "B087", "document_id": "0001193125-14-455030", "ordinal": 87, "start_line": 1622, "end_line": 1623, "raw_text": "On October 14, 2014, Mr. Fortnum called Mr. Malkoski to confirm the proposed price of $19.00 and discuss finalizing the draft\nmerger agreement and proceeding with the transaction as previously planned.", "clean_text": "On October 14, 2014, Mr. Fortnum called Mr. Malkoski to confirm the proposed price of $19.00 and discuss finalizing the draft merger agreement and proceeding with the transaction as previously planned.", "is_heading": false, "page_break_before": false, "page_break_after": false, "date_mentions": [{"raw_text": "October 14, 2014", "normalized": "2014-10-14", "precision": "exact_day"}], "entity_mentions": [], "evidence_density": 4, "temporal_phase": "outcome"}
{"block_id": "B088", "document_id": "0001193125-14-455030", "ordinal": 88, "start_line": 1625, "end_line": 1626, "raw_text": "Also on October 14, 2014, Perkins Coie and Sidley Austin\nexchanged successive drafts of the merger agreement and disclosure letter, and discussed the updated drafts, and Milbank and Sidley Austin finalized the voting and support agreement to be entered into by SEACOR.", "clean_text": "Also on October 14, 2014, Perkins Coie and Sidley Austin exchanged successive drafts of the merger agreement and disclosure letter, and discussed the updated drafts, and Milbank and Sidley Austin finalized the voting and support agreement to be entered into by SEACOR.", "is_heading": false, "page_break_before": false, "page_break_after": false, "date_mentions": [{"raw_text": "October 14, 2014", "normalized": "2014-10-14", "precision": "exact_day"}], "entity_mentions": [], "evidence_density": 2, "temporal_phase": "outcome"}
{"block_id": "B089", "document_id": "0001193125-14-455030", "ordinal": 89, "start_line": 1628, "end_line": 1630, "raw_text": "Later on October 14, 2014, Party A provided a formal letter with its indication of interest with respect to an acquisition of the Company\nat a price of $16.00 per share, citing increased volatility in the markets as the reason for the decrease in the offer price. Based on the $11.07 per share closing price of Penford\u0092s common stock as of October 13, 2014, the day immediately\nprior to receiving this indication of interest, the offer price of $16.00 per share represented a 45% premium.", "clean_text": "Later on October 14, 2014, Party A provided a formal letter with its indication of interest with respect to an acquisition of the Company at a price of $16.00 per share, citing increased volatility in the markets as the reason for the decrease in the offer price. Based on the $11.07 per share closing price of Penford\u0092s common stock as of October 13, 2014, the day immediately prior to receiving this indication of interest, the offer price of $16.00 per share represented a 45% premium.", "is_heading": false, "page_break_before": false, "page_break_after": false, "date_mentions": [{"raw_text": "October 14, 2014", "normalized": "2014-10-14", "precision": "exact_day"}, {"raw_text": "October 13, 2014", "normalized": "2014-10-13", "precision": "exact_day"}], "entity_mentions": [{"raw_text": "Party A", "entity_type": "party_alias"}, {"raw_text": "the Company", "entity_type": "party_alias"}], "evidence_density": 4, "temporal_phase": "outcome"}
